l beauty .</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">If a local authority or other highway authority refuses to ban motorized traffic from these lanes and byways, then individuals or groups should be able to challenge them and appeal.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">As things are, it is really upsetting to meet rowdy and sometimes dangerous cars and bikes along the paths mostly used by walkers and cyclists.  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">They are destructive of the paths and noisily out of place in these peaceful and beautiful areas.  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Tax-payers money is constantly being spent repairing green lanes damaged by off-roaders.  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Red tape is involved when agencies have to be pressured into doing these repairs and when rights of way claims have to be processed.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">The government is trying to save money,  and deregulate, is it not?  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">These requests would seem to be in keeping with those aims and contribute to the betterment of the environment for ourselves and our descendants.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Thank you for this opportunity to express </span><a name="_GoBack"></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">our views.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">September 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>